4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new method for improving the performance of person re-identification, which is an important application of AI. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as person re-identification has applications in security and surveillance.
